        {
            "title": "深圳公訴恒大案一審開庭 許家印當庭表示認罪 法健將擇期宣判",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新華網引述深圳市中級人民法院微信公眾號消息，指出恒大集團、恒大地產及許家印案一審已於近日開庭，許家印當庭認罪，法庭將擇期宣判。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20210915-CT-03333.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20210915-CT-03333.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道指，在4月13日至14日，廣東省深圳市中級人民法院對深圳市人民檢察院對恒大集團、恒大地產及恒大主席許家印的公訴，進行公開開庭審理。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">案件對恒大集團的指控包括非法吸收公眾存款、集資詐騙、違法發放貸款、欺詐發行證券、違規披露重要信息、單位行賄；對恒大地產指控是欺詐發行證券；對許家印指控包括非法吸收公眾存款、集資詐騙、違法發放貸款、違法運用資金、欺詐發行證券、違規披露重要信息、職務侵佔等。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道指，在庭審中，法庭主時控辯雙方圍繞指控的事實進行法庭調查及法庭辯論，被告單位、許家印進行了最後陳述。許家印當庭表示認罪悔罪；法庭將擇期宣判。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道又指，部份人大代表、政協委員、以及被告人親屬、集資參與人代表等亦有旁聽庭審。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15870404-%e6%b7%b1%e5%9c%b3%e5%85%ac%e8%a8%b4%e6%81%92%e5%a4%a7%e6%a1%88%e4%b8%80%e5%af%a9%e9%96%8b%e5%ba%ad-%e8%a8%b1%e5%ae%b6%e5%8d%b0%e7%95%b6%e5%ba%ad%e8%a1%a8%e7%a4%ba%e8%aa%8d%e7%bd%aa-%e6%b3%95%e5%81%a5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20231003_blog_-HSU_03333_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 12:41:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "KLN 公布三項高層任命",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">KLN Logistics Group Limited(00636)今天公佈三項高層管理人員的任命，旨在加速公司環球業務擴展，並強化其財務韌性。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"KLN 首席財務主管曹健麟(左)、KLN 首席營運主管黃兆龍(中)及KLN 首席人力資源主管沈暉(右 )。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_fi_00636_.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"KLN 首席財務主管曹健麟(左)、KLN 首席營運主管黃兆龍(中)及KLN 首席人力資源主管沈暉(右 )。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_fi_00636_.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">KLN 首席財務主管曹健麟(左)、KLN 首席營運主管黃兆龍(中)及KLN 首席人力資源主管沈暉(右 )。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">曹健麟於 2026 年 4 月 1 日獲委任為 KLN 首席財務主管，並將於 2026 年 5 月 21 日起獲委任為執行董事。他於會計、財務及內部監控方面擁有逾 25 年經驗，在加入 KLN 之前，於 2011 年至 2026 年期間為羅兵咸永道會計師事務所審計業務部合夥人。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">沈暉擔任首席人力資源主管，她在2026 年2月23日加入 KLN。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">KLN 首席營運主管黃兆龍將於2026年5月21日起獲委任為執行董事，將負責監督環球營運，推動各市場的營運整合與卓越服務。他具有逾25年環球運輸及物流行業經驗。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15870377-kln-%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%83%e4%b8%89%e9%a0%85%e9%ab%98%e5%b1%a4%e4%bb%bb%e5%91%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250828_FI_00636_FB_1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 12:27:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱升幅收窄 恒指升109點報25770點 寧德時代成藍籌包尾",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場憧憬美伊或展開下一輛直接會談，外圍股市乘勢反彈，港股今早則先升後回順，寧德時代(03750)受配股傳聞影響，早市成為表現最差藍籌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開268點，初段曾再往上衝，可惜在逼近26000點時卻「窒步」，最高報25995點，升334點後掉頭，開始拾級回吐的走勢，早市後段升幅曾收窄至不足100點，低位25748點時僅升87點，尾市持續於僅升約100點水平整固。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特微博影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260325_FI_source-web_09992-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特微博影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260325_FI_source-web_09992-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特微博影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240311_FI_source-web_寧德時代2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240311_FI_source-web_寧德時代2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特微博影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260325_FI_source-web_09992-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特微博影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240311_FI_source-web_寧德時代2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指中午收報25770點，升109點或0.43%。恒生科技指數跑輸大市，半日升8點或0.18%，報4830點；國企指數升25點或0.29%，報8627點。主板半日成交1214.03億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指半日升120點，報25785點，高水15點。科指期貨升19點，報4834點，高水4點。國指期貨升25點，報8626點，低水1點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股升多於跌，金融板塊是撐市主力。滙控(00005)升1.37%，報140.7元，為恒指提供近29點升幅。工商銀行(01398)創超過3年新高，升0.72%，報7.03元；中國銀行也漲0.99%，報5.09元，同系中銀香港(02388)更升2.2%，報44.58元，創1個月高位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兩隻藍籌內險股均漲逾1%，中國平安(02318)升1.78%，報62.75元；中國人壽(02628)則升1.55%，報27.48元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藍籌地產股全線報升，龍湖(00960)上月及首季合同銷售均按年跌逾五成，該股今早反而升5.22%，報8.06元，是表現次佳恒指成分股。藍籌升幅榜首則落入早市中段抽升的泡泡瑪特(09992)之手，該股今早擺脫近期弱勢，反彈6.01%，報160.6元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特微博影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260325_FI_source-web_09992-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特微博影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260325_FI_source-web_09992-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特微博影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科股個別發展，「ATMXJ」兩升三跌，當中以阿里巴巴(09988)表現最佳，半日升1.14%，報124.6元；京東(09618)也升0.45%，報112.8元。騰訊(00700)微跌0.25%，報488.8元；小米(01810)跌0.07%，報30.64元；美團(03690)則挫2.43%，報84.35元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代將於明天舉行董事會議決今年首季業績，在派成績表前應不會配股集資，但昨天收市後市場卻傳出該公司正就發行H股或換股債集資約50億美元的意向，探討投資者的興趣；該股今早即時受壓，A、H齊齊逆市回吐。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代A股(300750.SZ)今早跌勢尚算有限，半日僅跌0.59%，報424.61元人民幣。該公司H股的沽壓則明顯較大，最低曾見633元，挫7.25%；中午收報653元，跌幅收窄至4.32%，依然在藍籌中表現包尾，半日成交已達20.67億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240311_FI_source-web_寧德時代2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240311_FI_source-web_寧德時代2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地車股亦呈弱勢，比亞迪(01211)跌1.63%，報108.5元；吉利汽車(00175)跌0.96%，報24.7元；理想汽車(02015)更挫2.65%，報71.75元，在藍籌中排尾二。蔚來(09866)跌1.91%，報51.4元；小鵬汽車(09868)微跌0.22%，報67.45元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，嵐圖(07489)大股東擬入市增持H股，首期增持涉及不超過2.5億元人幣，支撐該股今早在車股中突圍而出，升2.8%，報6.25元，是10日高位。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15870357-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87109%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125770%e9%bb%9e-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e6%88%90%e8%97%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 12:21:36",
