        {
            "title": "新世界柏傲莊III單日售出逾50伙 套現逾12.8億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新世界發展(00017)與港鐵(00066)合作的港鐵大圍站上蓋「柏傲莊III THE PAVILIA FARM III 」單日沽出52伙大宅，套現逾12.8億。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"柏傲莊III 售樓情況\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_PP_PAVILIA-FARM_00017_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"柏傲莊III 售樓情況\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_PP_PAVILIA-FARM_00017_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">柏傲莊III 售樓情況</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">售出單位包括8伙四房雙套、15伙四房一套、29伙三房單位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">成交價及呎價最高一伙為第8座(8A)48樓A單位，屬四房雙套連工作間及洗手間設計，實用面積1210平方呎，成交價4356萬，呎價3.6萬。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">「柏傲莊III」是次採取「雙線銷售」策略，除了臨河三、四房單位採用招標形式發售，內園單位亦以價單形式發售。周四上載第1A號價單，集團稱｜現正與合作伙伴商討，研究短期內加推單位應市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">項目已取得滿意紙，現樓可以即買即住。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15870225-%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e6%9f%8f%e5%82%b2%e8%8e%8aiii%e5%96%ae%e6%97%a5%e5%94%ae%e5%87%ba%e9%80%be50%e4%bc%99-%e5%a5%97%e7%8f%be%e9%80%be12-8%e5%84%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_PP_PAVILIA-FARM_00017_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 11:51:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股揚升   深股升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日升，深股升逾1%，曾升1.5%，兩市成交合計14996.62億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日報4010點，升21點或0.55%，今早以4006點開市，升18點或0.46%。上午區間上落，最高見4011，升23點或0.58%，最低見3999，升11點或0.28%，為上午低位，半日成交6279.86億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日報14603﹐升195或1.36%，今早開市報14514點，亦升106點或0.74%，最低見14463，升56點或0.39%，即節節向上，高見14623，升216點或1.5%，半日成交8716.76億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日升38點或0.84%，報4685點，今早升29點或0.65%，開報4676點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日報3550，升73點或2.13%，今早開市報3507點，升30點或0.88%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15870204-a%e8%82%a1%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1",
